trans-unit.source: Parses a new URI scheme.
trans-unit.target: Analyserer en ny URI-skjemaet.

trans-unit.source: This is an abstract class.
trans-unit.target: Dette er en abstrakt klasse.

trans-unit.source: The UriParser class enables you to create parsers for new URI schemes.
trans-unit.target: Klassen UriParser lar deg opprette parsere for ny URI-adresseskjemaer.

trans-unit.source: You can write these parsers in their entirety, or the parsers can be derived from well-known schemes (HTTP, FTP, and other schemes based on network protocols).
trans-unit.target: Du kan skrive disse parsere i sin helhet, eller parsere kan utledes fra velkjente skjemaene (HTTP FTP og andre skjemaene som er basert på nettverksprotokoller).

trans-unit.source: If you want to create a completely new parser, inherit from <xref:System.GenericUriParser>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil opprette en helt ny parser, Arv fra <xref:System.GenericUriParser>.</xref:System.GenericUriParser>

trans-unit.source: If you want to create a parser that extends a well-known URI scheme, inherit from <xref:System.FtpStyleUriParser>, <xref:System.HttpStyleUriParser>, <xref:System.FileStyleUriParser>, <xref:System.GopherStyleUriParser>, or <xref:System.LdapStyleUriParser>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil opprette en parser som utvider en velkjente URI-skjemaet, arver fra <xref:System.FtpStyleUriParser>, <xref:System.HttpStyleUriParser>, <xref:System.FileStyleUriParser>, <xref:System.GopherStyleUriParser>, eller <xref:System.LdapStyleUriParser>.</xref:System.LdapStyleUriParser> </xref:System.GopherStyleUriParser> </xref:System.FileStyleUriParser> </xref:System.HttpStyleUriParser> </xref:System.FtpStyleUriParser>

trans-unit.source: Microsoft strongly recommends that you use a parser shipped with the .NET Framework.
trans-unit.target: Microsoft anbefaler at du bruker en parser levert med .NET Framework.

trans-unit.source: Building your own parser increases the complexity of your application, and will not perform as well as the shipped parsers.
trans-unit.target: Bygging av dine egne parseren økes kompleksiteten ved programmet, og vil ikke fungere i tillegg til de leverte parsere.

trans-unit.source: Use the GetComponents method to determine the value of various parts of the URI, such as the <xref:System.UriComponents>, <xref:System.UriComponents>, or <xref:System.UriComponents>.
trans-unit.target: Bruk GetComponents-metoden til å bestemme verdien for ulike delene av URI, som den <xref:System.UriComponents>, <xref:System.UriComponents>, eller <xref:System.UriComponents>.</xref:System.UriComponents> </xref:System.UriComponents> </xref:System.UriComponents>

trans-unit.source: The components are returned in the order that they appear in the URI.
trans-unit.target: Komponentene returneres i rekkefølgen som vises i URIEN.

trans-unit.source: For example, if <xref:System.UriComponents> is specified, it appears first.
